			<p>
				<strong>Bolivia is full of natural beauty.</strong> Home to some of the most breathtaking landscapes we had the pleasure of visiting, Bolivia is somewhere where you will get a <strong>completely authentic experience.</strong> Even the “touristy” areas of Bolivia are less touristy than most other cities we visited. For this reason it is amazing and difficult. Especially if this is the first country you are travelling to in South America, <strong>it will be a culture shock. </strong>
